name: i want sushi hair ties
description:
I Want Sushi “Ponytails” by insidesign

	Bad hair day? No more! Fabric button “Ponytails” by insidesign. Made with fabulous, quality fabric and Goody ‘Ouchless’ elastics. Hip and fresh, they are sure to add “delicious” to your “do”!

	Set of 3 “Ponytails” come on a snazzy insidesign card and professionally wrapped for gift-giving or to keep for yourself!

name: cute as a button ring
description:
“Cute as a Button Ring” by insidesign

	This little bauble is sure to make your finger smile, as it really is cute as a button! Made with fabulous, quality fabric and an adjustable ring. 
Très chic!

name: memory wire bracelet
description: One size fits all and once you wear the item a number of times, like a ring, it will conform to your body. So it “remembers” what size it needs to be in order to fit the wearer comfortably and securely. People with arthritis especially like memory wire jewelry because it’s so easy to put on and take off.
